# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# VAHDAM Mailer Studio — Environment Variables
# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# This file documents the env vars the app needs. Copy to `.env.local` for
# local `vercel dev` use, OR add the same vars in the Vercel dashboard for
# Production / Preview / Development environments.
#
# NEVER commit a populated `.env.local` — it's already in `.gitignore`.
# This `.env.example` IS committed (no real values, just placeholders).
# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# ─── REQUIRED — Server-side OpenAI calls (Create with AI, image gen, concepts) ───
# Get key:    https://platform.openai.com/api-keys
# Fund acct:  https://platform.openai.com/settings/organization/billing  ($5 min)
# Used by:    api/ai/generate.js + api/ai/image.js (both Vercel functions)
OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-proj-replace-with-real-key

# ─── OPTIONAL — Model pinning (sensible defaults if unset) ───
# Text model for brief generation, concept ideation, mailer planning, QA gate.
# Recommended: gpt-4o-mini (fastest + cheapest while still high-quality JSON)
# Alternatives: gpt-4o, gpt-4-turbo, gpt-4.1-mini
OPENAI_TEXT_MODEL=gpt-4o-mini

# Image model for hero photo generation. Currently gpt-image-1 is OpenAI's only
# native image API model; other names will return 404.
OPENAI_IMAGE_MODEL=gpt-image-1

# Provider selector — currently only 'openai' is honored. Reserved for future
# multi-provider routing (e.g. anthropic | openai | google).
APP_AI_PROVIDER=openai

# ─── OPTIONAL — Supabase (cross-device dashboard storage) ───
# If unset, the dashboard falls back to localStorage-only.
# Get from:   https://supabase.com/dashboard/project/_/settings/api
# SUPABASE_URL=https://xxxxx.supabase.co
# SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=eyJhbGciOi...

# ─── INTERNAL — set by Vercel automatically; do NOT override ───
# VERCEL=1
# VERCEL_ENV=production|preview|development
# VERCEL_URL=...
